始めたのならやり切る覚悟を
If you've started, be prepared to finish

1177
01:04:00,296 --> 01:04:03,696
敗者と勝者のDuet
A duet of winners and losers

1178
01:04:04,296 --> 01:04:07,896
劣等感弾き出された不条理の屑
Scraps of absurdity cast out by inferiority complexes

1179
01:04:08,096 --> 01:04:11,296
振り払え貪欲に志は消えない
Shake it off greedily; our will won't vanish

1180
01:04:11,296 --> 01:04:17,096
2人ならやれるさ
If it's the two of us, we can do it

1181
01:04:19,096 --> 01:04:22,096
生きるってなんだサボった者勝ちか
What does it mean to live? Is laziness the winner?

1182
01:04:22,096 --> 01:04:24,096
そんなもの握りつぶせ
Crush thoughts like that

1183
01:04:24,096 --> 01:04:25,896
上辺じゃいられない
I can't stay on the surface

1184
01:04:25,896 --> 01:04:27,896
エンタメライダー
Entertainment Rider

1185
01:04:27,896 --> 01:04:29,496
人生賭け　駆け抜け
Betting my life as I run through

1186
01:04:29,496 --> 01:04:30,896
絶望も栄光も
Through both despair and glory

1187
01:04:30,896 --> 01:04:32,896
Lemme see you fight back

1188
01:04:32,896 --> 01:04:36,496
どうなったって何も変わらないんだって
Saying nothing changes no matter what happens

1189
01:04:36,696 --> 01:04:39,896
ミームされた現実に囚われて
Trapped in a memed reality

1190
01:04:40,096 --> 01:04:42,896
This life where we're stuck taking chances

1191
01:04:43,096 --> 01:04:45,596
飽き飽きしてんでしょ？？
You're sick of it, aren't you??

1192
01:04:46,096 --> 01:04:48,896
We're living in a world with no direction

1193
01:04:49,096 --> 01:04:52,896
Reach out with our light 'till we make a connection

1194
01:04:53,096 --> 01:04:54,896
Tearing the walls apart

1195
01:04:54,896 --> 01:04:56,896
Facing it all, side by side

1196
01:04:57,096 --> 01:04:59,096
Once again, it's us against the world

1197
01:05:00,904 --> 01:05:01,404
舐めんじゃねーよ
Don't underestimate us!

1198
01:05:01,404 --> 01:05:03,504
本能をヒリつかせて
Let your instincts tingle,

1199
01:05:03,504 --> 01:05:07,504
本物見せつけろ
and show them the real thing!

1200
01:05:07,504 --> 01:05:08,804
圧倒
Overwhelming...

1201
01:05:08,804 --> 01:05:09,504
絶頂
climax!

1202
01:05:09,504 --> 01:05:13,604
アンバランスを踊れ
Dance the unbalance!

1203
01:05:15,604 --> 01:05:16,904
踊れ
Dance!

1204
01:05:18,304 --> 01:05:20,104
踊れ
Dance!

1205
01:05:21,104 --> 01:05:26,604
踊れ
Dance!

1206
01:05:29,604 --> 01:05:32,104
Thanks for watching everyone! Thank you to my guests!

1207
01:05:32,104 --> 01:05:34,104
Thank you to the band! Thank you everyone!

1208
01:05:34,104 --> 01:05:36,104
Come hang out at members gentei!
Come hang out at the members-only after-show!

1209
01:05:36,104 --> 01:05:37,604
Okay, 後のもよろしく！
Okay, look forward to the rest!

1210
01:05:37,604 --> 01:05:39,104
Yeah, and 5 is good!

1211
01:05:39,104 --> 01:05:41,604
That's about all you guys, I'm Mori Calliope, peace out, see ya!

1212
01:05:46,104 --> 01:05:48,104
Woo! Let's go! Yeah!

1213
01:05:48,104 --> 01:05:50,104
Bye!

1214
01:05:52,604 --> 01:05:56,604
Hah, what's up you crazy skeleton...

1215
01:05:57,104 --> 01:06:00,104
Mori Calliope Birthday 2026
[Visual: Mori Calliope Birthday 2026]

1216
01:06:00,104 --> 01:06:03,104
I mean, dearest deadbeats, the hour is finally upon us.

1217
01:06:03,104 --> 01:06:08,104
The sale of Mori Calliope's birthday celebration goods is about to begin.

1218
01:06:08,604 --> 01:06:13,104
誕生日記念 2026
[Visual: Birthday Celebration 2026]

1219
01:06:09,104 --> 01:06:13,104
On this most auspicious day, you've been granted a great blessing by Death herself.

1220
01:06:13,104 --> 01:06:17,604
A most fortunate occurrence for thee, that such a glorious chest should appear before thine eyes.

1221
01:06:17,604 --> 01:06:21,104
Let's take a peek at what the Goddess of Death herself has to offer, shall we?

1222
01:06:21,604 --> 01:06:28,104
The journey ahead is long and arduous. It would do thee good to prepare for it with such luxurious treasures.

1223
01:06:29,604 --> 01:06:34,104
死の永遠の寵愛に抱かれて - ブランケット
[Embraced by Death's Eternal Favor - Blanket]

1224
01:06:30,104 --> 01:06:34,104
Firstly, wouldst thou find comfort in dear Death's embrace? If it be so...

1225
01:06:34,104 --> 01:06:40,104
...take some warmth along thy journey with this very large rollable blanket featuring a most intimidating maiden.

1226
01:06:40,604 --> 01:06:45,104
Yours truly, designed by my favorite dark fantasy artist, Shimhag! Woo!

1227
01:06:45,104 --> 01:06:52,104
The maiden in question possesses artworks en masse from this particular individual, so I'd be most elated if you bought it.

1228
01:06:52,104 --> 01:06:57,104
Lay it across your bed, hang it on your wall, take it with you on an outing, think of the possibilities!

1229
01:07:00,104 --> 01:07:04,104
死の祝福の護符 - ランダムラバーストラップ
[Amulet of Death's Blessing - Random Rubber Strap]

1230
01:07:00,104 --> 01:07:04,104
Secondly, whilst on thy noble journey, thou mayst come to need a spark of aid.

1231
01:07:04,104 --> 01:07:09,104
If it be so, take one of these amulets. The emblem of a knight to boost your strength.

1232
01:07:09,104 --> 01:07:13,104
The emblem of a samurai to grant you additional dexterity.

1233
01:07:13,104 --> 01:07:17,104
The emblem of a priestess to bestow additional health to thy weary body.

1234
01:07:17,604 --> 01:07:23,104
And lastly, the emblem of a necromancer to grant thee additional intelligence.

1235
01:07:23,104 --> 01:07:27,104
Alas, as fortune be a fickle mistress, thou may only receive one in a set.

1236
01:07:27,604 --> 01:07:30,604
I pray thee be granted the boon most favorable to thy quest.

1237
01:07:30,604 --> 01:07:35,104
Or, or you could just purchase them all separately if you're looking to speedrun the experience, I suppose.

1238
01:07:37,104 --> 01:07:42,104
幸運の休息のランタン
[Lantern of Fortunate Respite]

1239
01:07:37,104 --> 01:07:42,104
Thirdly, I present to thee the shining centerpiece of this valuable collection.

1240
01:07:42,104 --> 01:07:48,104
Take a moment of repose and sit beside this warm and healing light, granted unto thee by Death herself.

1241
01:07:48,604 --> 01:07:54,104
A lantern to revive thee as many times as needed throughout even the most daunting of journeys.

1242
01:07:55,104 --> 01:08:00,104
May it light thy way to victory, or to sweet dreams, whichever is preferred.

1243
01:08:00,104 --> 01:08:04,104
Enjoy an elegant design chosen specifically by myself.

1244
01:08:05,604 --> 01:08:10,104
再生の癒しのグラス
[Healing Flask of Regeneration (Glass)]

1245
01:08:05,604 --> 01:08:10,104
And of course, how could one continue a journey into vast and unforgiving lands without a source of healing?

1246
01:08:10,604 --> 01:08:17,104
Rejuvenate thyself with this generous flask, or rather glass, that seems to refill endlessly upon rest at your lantern.

1247
01:08:17,604 --> 01:08:24,104
At least, I think it will. There really are no guarantees in this life, but give it a try yourself.

1248
01:08:24,604 --> 01:08:29,104
Enjoy your favorite beverage during a night of exploring your favorite fantasy scenarios.

1249
01:08:31,604 --> 01:08:36,104
シチュエーションボイス: 「失われた者への死の神聖なる裁き」
[Situational Voice: "Divine Sanction Upon the Lost One"]

1250
01:08:31,604 --> 01:08:36,104
But naturally, it'd do me no good to leave thee without, I don't know, a bedtime story.

1251
01:08:36,104 --> 01:08:42,104
To put this enchanting collection into context, so please enjoy a short audiobook-style recording of a fantastical story.

1252
01:08:43,104 --> 01:08:49,104
Believe it or not, we are the stars of this tale, so enjoy it on a rainy evening wrapped warmly in Death's embrace.

1253
01:08:49,604 --> 01:08:56,104
The, the blanket I mean. You can use the flask also for drinking at the same time. You should really buy the full set.

1254
01:08:57,604 --> 01:09:03,104
フルセット購入特典
[Full Set Purchase Bonus]

1255
01:08:57,604 --> 01:09:03,104
And definitely do, because lucky skeletons who act fast and purchase the entire set will be granted a hand-signed postcard...

1256
01:09:03,104 --> 01:09:08,104
...with a special color variant of Shimhag's masterpiece rendition of Death herself.

1257
01:09:08,604 --> 01:09:13,604
The hand-signed option is in limited supply, so you must be swift.

1258
01:09:14,104 --> 01:09:19,604
For those that are unable to secure this extremely rare offering in time, do not fret.

1259
01:09:19,604 --> 01:09:22,104
By purchasing the entire set, a duplicated foil-stamped signature postcard will be sent as a bonus.

1260
01:09:22,104 --> 01:09:26,604
That is all from me, Death's maiden and dark fantasy enjoyer, Mori Calliope.

1261
01:09:26,604 --> 01:09:32,104
This year's goods are very different, but I wanted to pay tribute to a genre that I love so dearly...

1262
01:09:32,104 --> 01:09:36,604
...and has really made every day of my job so wonderful and happy.

1263
01:09:36,604 --> 01:09:41,104
I am so grateful to you guys for coming to enjoy my show as well.

1264
01:09:41,104 --> 01:09:44,104
Comment and let me know what your favorite part was.

1265
01:09:44,104 --> 01:09:46,604
Be sure to like the concert so others may be recommended it, and subscribe if you enjoy Mori Calliope.

1266
01:09:46,604 --> 01:09:48,604
With that, I bid thee farewell.

1267
01:09:48,604 --> 01:09:52,104
And Happy Birthday to me!!

1268
01:10:00,112 --> 01:10:05,112
Happy Birthday to me!!

1269
01:10:05,112 --> 01:10:11,112
6 birthdays high?! This time was even more
special than usual.

1270
01:10:11,112 --> 01:10:18,112
Much love to my guests, my Dead Beats, my band,
and everyone who wants to see me fly!

1271
01:10:18,112 --> 01:10:25,112
Let's have an even happier year together!!

